Explanation:

The first-order correction $chevron.l n | H' | n chevron.r$ only survives for terms that preserve particle number. Evaluating the central term yields $2gamma chevron.l n | (a^dagger)^3 a^3 | n chevron.r = 2gamma n(n-1)(n-2)$.
